    <li><a href="https://istex.is/en/vorur/lettlopi/">Léttlopin värikartta</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://lopidesign.is/en/shop/adults/sweaters/riddari/">Riddarin ohje</a></li>
  </ul>
</section>
